<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1331241-what-was-so-important-about-terry-lennox-s">What was so important about Terry Lennox&#39;s pigskin suitcase, that it received so much attention in the early part of the story and never reappeared?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1331241'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F2054.The_Long_Goodbye">like</a></span>

